Stringer Davis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stringer_Davis 0 James Buckley Stringer Davis, generally known as Stringer Davis (4 June 1899 – 29 August 1973), was an English character actor on the stage and in films and a British army officer who served in both world wars. He was married to actress Margaret Rutherford.
